headline: 2 Reasons to Watch RSG and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Since May 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 100%. But one standout stock has doubled the market - over the past five years, Republic Services has surged 199% to $245.57 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 17.5% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 17.1%.
